     tt-date at 17 FORMAT "99/99/99"
     tt-amt AT 33 format "->>,>>>,>>9.99"
     tt-vend at 59 space(1)
     tt-name
     with frame f1 DOWN width 132 no-box NO-LABELS NO-ATTR-SPACE.

